<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>762</hymn_number>
<author>W.H. Doane</author>
<title>Modia, modia FFPM762</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Modia, modia,
 Fandrao very tokoa,
 Fa ny efitra be
 No diavina izao ;
 Ry zanako ô !
 Modia izao.

[V2]
 Modia, modia,
 Fa miandry ny Ray
 Hampandroso anao
 Sady hanome soa ;
 Ry zanako ô !
 Modia izao.

[V3]
 Modia, modia,
 Fa nanavotra anao
 Jeso ilay be fitia
 Izay nisolo anao ;
 Ry zanako ô !
 Modia izao.

[V4]
 Modia, modia,
 Ka ilaozy izao
 Izay ratsy natao
 Nahameloka anao,
 Ry zanako ô !
 Modia izao.

[V5]
 Modia, modia,
 Hovantaninao ao
 Ny tranon'ny Ray
 Sy ny lamba madio
 Ry zanako ô !
 Modia izao.</lyrics>
</song>